<lb ed="GA" n="0260a12"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="5"><cb:jhead>洛陽伽藍記卷<note n="0260a1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">第【CB】，弟【志彙】</note><app n="0260a1201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">第</lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">弟</rdg></app>五</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
